<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-09T13:30:36-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-09T13:30:36-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T13:30:36-04:00</updated><title> Apple Watch 即将推出睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;事件幻灯片，显示 Apple 通过 Apple Watch 检测到“可能存在睡眠呼吸暂停”的警告通知。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XKvdVTCaD0_Gnakb5YWAzJd8x3o=/0x51:997x716/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574344/lcimg_bf067d6e_79ae_4512_94 ec_4cd461543748.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;b0cez5&quot;>;Apple 正在为 Apple Watch 添加睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能。 Apple Watch Series 9 即将推出新功能，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features- release-date&quot;>;刚刚发布的 Series 10&lt;/a>; 和 Apple Watch Ultra 2，Apple 在周一的产品活动中宣布。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;xsqTsd&quot;>;睡眠呼吸暂停是&lt;a href= “https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/sleep-apnea/symptoms-causes/syc-20377631&quot;>;一种导致您在睡眠时停止呼吸的疾病&lt;/a>;。睡眠呼吸暂停是可穿戴设备制造商已经研究了一段时间的一项功能，三星已获得 FDA 批准，可以通过 Galaxy Watch 进行睡眠呼吸暂停跟踪 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/ 9/24067819/samsung-galaxy-watch-sleep-apnea-tracker-fda-de-novo-authorization&quot;>;今年早些时候&lt;/a>;。苹果表示，它正在使用手表上的加速计来监控一项新指标，该指标被称为“呼吸障碍”。您将能够在“健康”应用中查看您的夜间呼吸障碍值。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;gkDI9V&quot;>;该公司预计其睡眠呼吸暂停将获得 FDA 批准...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep-apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt; /a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep-apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240045/apple-watch-sleep-apnea-detection-feature-series-9-10-ultra-2</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T13:24:41-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T13:24:41-04:00</updated><title> Apple Watch Ultra 2 现已推出黑色</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/M3sEf7VuMb3lQ7KUg3KH4-Fv8d8=/1x0:1600x1066/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73574323/lcimg_925c21d9_cd9b_4a65_a6de_0826afceb3b4.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;黑色 Apple Watch Ultra 2。&lt;/em>; |照片：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7gEGfC&quot;>;Apple 更新了 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/3/24170798/该公司今天在 9 月份的活动中宣布，could-the-quest-3s-arrive-in-september&quot;>;Apple Watch Ultra 2&lt;/a>; 具有新的“缎光黑”颜色选项和睡眠呼吸暂停检测功能。自两年前推出以来，这是苹果首次为 Watch Ultra 提供多种颜色。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MNT6Gk&quot;>;Watch Ultra 2 将使用手表的加速计和随时间的测量来检测睡眠者的运动何时与睡眠呼吸暂停一致。该功能即将在新款 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date&quot;>;Apple 上推出Watch Series 10&lt;/a>; 以及 Series 9。Apple 还发布了全新钛金属米兰尼斯表带。售价 799 美元，今天即可预订，9 月 20 日发布。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;屏幕截图：Apple&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;RR7psL&quot;>; Watch Ultra 将获得 watchOS 11，其中包含以下更新：&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239740/apple-watch -ultra-specs-price-features-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239740/apple-watch-ultra-specs-price-features-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239740/apple-watch-ultra-specs-price-features-release-date</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T13:10:42-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T13:10:42-04:00</updated><title> Apple Watch Series 10 发布，屏幕更大、设计更薄</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;新款 Apple Watch Series 10 的图片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/R-5b9tJhokVkmqRPCKmrgsS-_vo=/1x0:2056x1370/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574301/apple.0。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;屏幕截图：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ePBofa&quot;>;Apple Watch 的第 10 版已在周一的 Apple 活动中发布，其广角亮度提高了 40% OLED 屏幕比 Apple Watch Ultra 上的显示屏更大。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;w2Qb4Y&quot;>;新款 Apple Watch Series 10 厚度仅为 9.7 毫米，比 Apple Watch Series 9 薄 10%。 Apple表示其更大的 OLED 屏幕（迄今为止 Apple Watch 中使用的最大尺寸）允许可穿戴设备在屏幕上显示额外的一行文本，使用户更容易一目了然地检查电子邮件和消息。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= “jMda7I&quot;>;Series 10 采用 Apple 全新 S10 芯片和四核神经引擎，采用抛光铝质表面，并采用集成智能手表各种天线的新型金属背板。它仍然防水...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs- features-release-date&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236801/apple-watch-series-10-price-specs-features-release-date</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T12:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T12:30:00-04:00</updated><title> “现在是 Glowtime”：苹果 iPhone 16 发布会的所有新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple 活动中彩虹色、发光的 Apple 徽标的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ICtQMvEJOW7cpu2X7O08cyBRkZ8=/134x0:2189x1370/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574202/Screenshot_2024_09_07_at_4.14.2 9_PM.0.png &quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Apple 的“It&#39;s Glowtime”iPhone 16 活动即将来临。&lt;/em>; |屏幕截图：YouTube&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;自 9 月份宣布 Apple Intelligence 推出以来，苹果推出的首款新手机。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 9/9/24237601/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-products&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-products" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24237601/apple-iphone-16-event-announcements-products</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name><name>边缘员工</name><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name><name>宋茜</name><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T12:30:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T12:30:00-04:00</updated><title> iPhone 16 活动直播博客：苹果主题演讲的所有新闻</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在石灰绿色背景上描绘几个 Apple 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8_BDOqOtMKP-OTUzrXgR1YdFLb8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574192/VRG_Illo_5258_K_Radtke_WWDC.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Kristen Radtke / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们为您提供有关 Apple Intelligence、iPhone、Apple Watch 和 AirPods 的最新信息。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236176/apple-iphone-16-liveblog-apple-watch-x-airpods-keynote&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/ p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236176/apple-iphone-16-liveblog-apple-watch-x-airpods-keynote" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24236176/apple-iphone-16-liveblog-apple-watch-x-airpods-keynote</id><author><name>边缘员工</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T11:46:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T11:46:53-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊允许 Audible 旁白通过人工智能克隆自己</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色、橙色和奶油色背景上的 Audible 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QMW4QmGaQvDXd8RXRBSNZFVWZJ8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574084/acastro_STK074_audible_04.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;仅限美国的 Beta 测试仅限于“一小群叙述者”。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;i1Rf0Z&quot;>;亚马逊本周将开始邀请一小群 Audible 叙述者来训练人工智能生成的语音克隆人，目的是加快速度为该平台制作有声读物。仅限美国的 Beta 测试&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.acx.com/mp/blog/now-in-beta-narrator-voice-replicas-on-acx&quot;>;在 Audible 的创作者市场上宣布&lt;/ a>; 据亚马逊称，“今年晚些时候”将扩展到作者、代理商和出版商等权利持有者。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Aps7Ue&quot;>;“有大量的图书目录尚未发布亚马逊在其声明中表示：“音频存在于音频中，当我们探索如何让更多书籍在 Audible 上栩栩如生时，我们致力于深思熟虑地平衡作者、叙述者、出版商和听众的利益。”测试版参与者将提交录音来训练他们的人工智能副本，并将保留...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239903/ amazon-audible-audiobook-narrators-ai- generated-voice-clones&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239903/amazon-audible-audiobook-narrators-ai-generated-voice-clones" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239903/amazon-audible-audiobook-narrators-ai- generated-voice-clones</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T11:41:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T11:41:17-04:00</updated><title> Meta Quest 3S 在 Meta 自己的 PC 应用程序中泄露</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Meta Quest Link PC 应用程序文件夹中看到的 Meta Quest 3S 的图片。与 Quest 3 类似，但前面不是三个药丸状传感器，而是六个聚集在一起的传感器封面的左右半部分各有两个。” src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ClN7EGjS2q2iEUnFoNYV4904fvg=/338x0:1375x691/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574071/Meta_Quest_3S.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Meta Quest 3S 的明显图像。&lt;/em>; |图片：Meta&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uSVFTA&quot;>;Meta 似乎已经泄露了 Meta Quest 3S，传闻其预算是去年的后续产品 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/23906313/meta-quest-3-review-vr-mixed-reality-headset&quot;>;Quest 3 耳机&lt;/a>;，位于其自己的 Windows Meta Quest Link PC 软件中。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.uploadvr.com/multiple-new-quest-3s-images-leak/&quot;>;UploadVR 发现&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，图像&lt;a href= “https://www.reddit.com/r/OculusQuest/comments/1fapa9v/official_image_of_the_quest_3s_found_in_the_files/&quot;>;发布在 Reddit&lt;/a>; 上，展示了一款在视觉上有点介于 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/21437674/oculus-quest-2-review-features-photos&quot;>;Quest 2&lt;/a>; 和 Quest 3。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;W2UEoB&quot;>;耳机预计&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/3/24170798/could-the-quest-3s-arrive-in-september&quot;>;使其首次获得 Meta 认可&lt;/a>;很快，该公司将于 9 月 25 日开始举办 Connect 活动。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;fQVgua&quot;>;“Quest 3S”（如果以该名称发货）似乎有前置摄像头。与 Quest 3 上的三个药丸状相机切口不同，它们在设备前盖上分成两组，每组三个，而表带保持不变。我仍然可以找到深埋在资源文件夹中的图像...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239819/meta-quest-3s -leak-budget-vr-headset&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239819/meta-quest-3s-leak-budget-vr-headset" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24239819/meta-quest-3s-leak-budget-vr-headset</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-09T11:17:39-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-09T11:17:39-04:00</updated><title>谷歌最新一代 Pixel 8 Pro 售价新低 624 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;海湾蓝色的 Google Pixel 8 Pro，在青色蓝色背景上显示后面板，周围环绕着透明的蓝色方块&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/X0UwbPa7Hne_sNGBYPIgJ82GTcM=/0x0 :2000x1333/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73574010/DSC05679.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Allison Johnson / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id =&quot;Tvhqb1&quot;>;可能是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event-september-iphone-16-date-time-live-stream-watch -how-to-rumors&quot;>;iPhone 16 发布日&lt;/a>;，但现在 Android 粉丝有很多优惠。现在，所有版本的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24225221/google-pixel-9-pro-xl-review-ai-gemini-screen-battery-camera&quot;>;Google Pixel 9&lt; /a>; 已广泛使用（包括出色的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24237586/google-pixel-9-pro-fold-review-screen-camera-battery&quot;>;Pixel 9 Pro Fold&lt;/a>;），去年的 &lt;strong>;Pixel 8 Pro&lt;/strong>; 在 &lt;a href=&quot;h